OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775624629
OL,3,CKatie Price banned from driving again
OL,4,Cover 80mph speeding ticket
OL,6,FKatie Price has been banned from
OL,7,Fdriving for the seventh time after
OL,8,Ffailing to respond to police letters
OL,9,Fabout an 80mph speeding ticket.
OL,11,FThe former glamour model, 47, has
OL,12,Freceived bans totalling more than six
OL,13,Fyears since she was first disqualified
OL,14,Fin 2010.
OL,16,FHer latest run-in with the law comes
OL,17,Fafter a Ford Capri registered in her
OL,18,Fname was caught at 80mph on the A64
OL,19,Fnear to the North Yorkshire village of
OL,20,FStutton.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775624629
OL,3,CKatie Price banned from driving again
OL,4,Cover 80mph speeding ticket
OL,6,FNorth Yorkshire Police wrote to Price
OL,7,Fat her home in West Sussex, asking her
OL,8,Fto confirm if she was driving the
OL,9,Fspeeding car.
OL,11,FShe has now been prosecuted and
OL,12,Fconvicted of failing to respond to
OL,13,Fpolice, landing her with a six-month
OL,14,Fdriving ban and a legal bill topping
OL,15,F#1,000.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775624629
OL,3,CKatie Price banned from driving again
OL,4,Cover 80mph speeding ticket
OL,6,FIn December 2010, Price was banned for
OL,7,Fsix months after admitting a speeding
OL,8,Fcharge, she was disqualified for a
OL,9,Fyear in 2012 after failing to respond
OL,10,Fto speeding tickets, and she received
OL,11,Fanother six-month ban in February 2018
OL,12,Fafter being caught speeding.
OL,14,FIn January 2019, she was in court
OL,15,Fagain to admit driving while
OL,16,Fdisqualified, leading to a three-month
OL,17,Fban.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775624629
OL,3,CKatie Price banned from driving again
OL,4,Cover 80mph speeding ticket
OL,6,FAnd just a month later she was
OL,7,Fconvicted by a judge of being drunk in
OL,8,Fcharge of a vehicle when it was seen
OL,9,Fby police to veer off the road and hit
OL,10,Fa grass verge.
OL,12,FPrice claimed that a mystery man had
OL,13,Fbeen at the wheel and left the scene
OL,14,Fbefore officers arrived, but a judge
OL,15,Fconcluded her evidence was "not
OL,16,Fplausible".
OL,26,@wD@\OUxD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
