PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775624629
OL,3,CKatie Price banned from driving again
OL,4,Cover 80mph speeding ticket
OL,6,FLater in 2019, Price was convicted of
OL,7,Ffailing to disclose the name of the
OL,8,Fdriver following a car crash, which
OL,9,Fled to her receiving an 18-month road
OL,10,Fban.
OL,12,FAnd in 2021, a judge condemned Price
OL,13,Ffor "one of the worst driving records
OL,14,FI have ever seen", as she was given a
OL,15,F16-week suspended prison sentence for
OL,16,Fdrink-driving while disqualified and
OL,17,Fwithout insurance.
OL,19,FPrice had flipped her car and told
OL,20,Fpolice at the scene: "I took drugs, I
OL,21,Fshould not be driving, I admit it all."
OL,26,@uD@EOUvD@QO]|D@VOU}D@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
