PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775624629
OL,3,CKatie Price banned from driving again
OL,4,Cover 80mph speeding ticket
OL,6,FThe incident landed her with a two-
OL,7,Fyear driving ban, as well as 100 hours
OL,8,Fof community service and up to 30
OL,9,Frehabilitation sessions.
OL,11,F"You appear to think you are above the
OL,12,Flaw," District Judge Amanda Kelly told
OL,13,Fher at the time.
OL,15,FIn 2024, Price was fined #880 for
OL,16,Fdriving without a licence and
OL,17,Finsurance in Northamptonshire, but she
OL,18,Fwas spared a ban for those offences.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775624629
OL,3,CKatie Price banned from driving again
OL,4,Cover 80mph speeding ticket
OL,6,FPrice's latest conviction and driving
OL,7,Fdisqualification was dealt with last
OL,8,Fweek in the Single Justice Procedure,
OL,9,Fa secretive court process where
OL,10,Fmagistrates deal with criminal cases
OL,11,Fbehind closed doors.
OL,13,FCourt papers show Price was charged
OL,14,Fwith speeding and failing to give
OL,15,Finformation relating to the
OL,16,Fidentification of the driver of a
OL,17,Fvehicle.
OL,19,FThe Ford Capri was caught on a speed
OL,20,Fcamera on a 70mph stretch of the A64
OL,21,Fat 3.03pm on October 15 last year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775624629
OL,3,CKatie Price banned from driving again
OL,4,Cover 80mph speeding ticket
OL,6,FShe was sent a police letter about the
OL,7,Fincident on October 20, and a reminder
OL,8,Fon November 10, warning her of looming
OL,9,Fcriminal proceedings.
OL,11,FHowever the police force said no
OL,12,Fresponse was received to either letter.
OL,14,FMagistrate Claire Sagar, sitting at
OL,15,FHarrogate Magistrates' Court last
OL,16,FTuesday, found Price guilty of the
OL,17,Ffailure to respond to police charge,
OL,18,Fordering her to pay a #660 fine, #120
OL,19,Fin costs, and a #264 victim surcharge.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775624629
OL,3,CKatie Price banned from driving again
OL,4,Cover 80mph speeding ticket
OL,6,FDue to the secretive nature of the
OL,7,Fcourt process, it is not known if
OL,8,FPrice was given the chance to argue
OL,9,Fagainst another driving ban, it is
OL,10,Funclear whether the court knew of her
OL,11,Fprevious driving record, and the
OL,12,Frecords do not reveal if she already
OL,13,Fhad penalty points on her licence.
OL,15,FThe speeding charge was withdrawn by
OL,16,Fthe police.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
